    <li>
      <Link href="https://github.com/eliheuer/caskaydia-cove" class="hover:underline">caskaydia-cove</Link><span class="text-muted-foreground"> — Caskaydia Cove is a fork of the Cascadia Code typeface with the RFN (Reserved Font Name) removed, plus small adjustments to conform to the Google Fonts spec.</span>
    </li>
    <li>
      <Link href="https://github.com/eliheuer/hasubi-mono" class="hover:underline">hasubi-mono</Link><span class="text-muted-foreground"> — A horizontal contrast monospace typeface designed by Eli Heuer. This is an alpha quality pre-1.0 typeface, not ready for use and currently under development. 🚧</span>
    </li>
    <li>
      <Link href="https://github.com/eliheuer/micro-grotesk" class="hover:underline">micro-grotesk</Link><span class="text-muted-foreground"> — ⚠️ Work in progress: A 256 UPM typeface in the smallest possible file size.</span>
